title: Fast Five: Jay & Scott Fight, Hug, Talk Sports…The Usual [Video]
text:
Fast Five: Jay & Scott Fight, Hug, Talk Sports…The Usual [Video] By Scott Prather October 15, 2015 3:13 AM Share on Twitter 
Another week brings another episode of FAST FIVE. As Jay and I watch our favorite major league baseball teams battle in the playoffs (GO METS!), we exchanged blows last week. This week, we…hug it out? Well, there is one cause that’s worth hugging for. 
However, before the hug comes a heated sports debate. Why does Jay hate the Saints? Will LSU’s Leonard Fournette run wild against Florida? What does the Cajun football team’s key to success have in common with one of Jay’s eating habits? It’s all part of this week’s episode of FAST FIVE.
